data.description: HOME IS BACK ON THE MARKET DUE TO BUYERS INABILITY TO SECURE FINANCING. Welcome to this charming residence nestled in the heart of Applewood. This traditional home offers a harmonious blend of timeless design and modern comforts, presenting an ideal opportunity for those seeking a balance between classic elegance and contemporary living. With 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 well-appointed bathrooms, this home effortlessly accommodates your family's needs and provides ample space for comfortable living. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a warm and inviting ambiance that exudes the character of a traditional home. Hardwood floors, intricate moldings, and thoughtful detailing contribute to the overall aesthetic. The living areas are perfect for gatherings and relaxation, while the well-equipped kitchen stands ready to inspire your culinary creations. One of the highlights of this property is the stunning backyard. Step outside to a generous outdoor oasis that invites you to unwind and entertain. Whether you're hosting barbecues, gardening, or simply enjoying the Colorado sunshine, the backyard offers a peaceful retreat that complements the indoor living spaces. The master suite of this home features a large walk-in closet, providing you with abundant storage space and organization options. Additionally, the master bathroom has been beautifully remodeled, showcasing a modern shower that offers a luxurious escape at the end of the day. Located in Wheat Ridge, you'll enjoy the convenience of urban amenities while being able to retreat to the tranquility of your private abode. This sought-after community offers a range of local shops, restaurants, parks, providing a well-rounded lifestyle for residents of all ages.
